{"tid":637360,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有時候真係好後悔中學冇拍過拖。","createTime":"2018-04-21T17:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T04:20:56.000Z","uid":136681,"like":41,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"40ab954d85b893e7ffc66d811ef82a4aa32c6750","tid":637360,"uid":136681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:27:08.000Z","msg":"中學拍拖，可以日日見面，向同一個目標努力，少好多顧慮。<br />\n同而家男朋友係中同，畢咗業先一齊。<br />\n佢中學時同過其他人拍拖。<br />\n我每次諗到佢最青春最純真嘅時光已經同第二個渡過咗，有好多第一次佢已經着住校服同第二個做咗。<br />\n我就會好傷心好傷心，忍唔住諗點解嗰個唔係我。<br />\n我知道咁樣諗係自尋煩惱同痛苦、對自己係種折磨，但係我真係控制唔到自己嘅想法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36645ed6ea726cc9c313210796c4a2adf9381376","tid":637360,"uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:30:46.000Z","msg":"遺憾編織出人生"},{"pid":"ebdbed251b1d1fb100b768f429d50c4d6dd4942e","tid":637360,"uid":174488,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:35:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"399685f4812c115874d5d03763c82b2a9d34f876","tid":637360,"uid":136681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36645ed6ea726cc9c313210796c4a2adf9381376","tid":637360,"uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:30:46.000Z","msg":"遺憾編織出人生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:44:18.000Z","msg":"遺憾當時年紀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de94ef6cc591e1b7e011f05a990783a3d6aab0f9","tid":637360,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人生"},{"pid":"6ae045b8db96f46b9a16ebf788fa1628410877a9","tid":637360,"uid":180402,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:46:22.000Z","msg":"係咪睇得多台劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"